Szeged.title: Szeged
Szeged.byline: Szeged is a Hungarian city in the Csongrád-Csanád County.

Szentendre.title: Szentendre
Szentendre.byline: Szentendre (Serbian: Сентандреја, Croatian: Senandrija, Ancient Latin: Ulcisia Castra) is a town in the Danube Bend region, on the right (western) bank of the Danube, 19 km north of Budapest.

Szentgotthárd.title: Szentgotthárd
Szentgotthárd.byline: Szentgotthárd (Slovenian: Monošternek, German: St. Gotthard) is in Vas County.
